FBIS4-63777 "drsov101_e_94012" FBIS-SOV-94-101 Daily Report 24 May 1994 UKRAINE International Affairs Ostankino Correspondents Stripped of Accreditation Ostankino Correspondents Stripped of Accreditation LD2405163694 Moscow NTV in Russian 1500 GMT 24 May 94 LD2405163694 Moscow NTV Russian BFN [Text] The Ukrainian Foreign Ministry has taken the decision to strip journalists from the Ostankino Television and Radio Company working on Ukrainian territory of their accreditation. The ministry accuses these journalists of provocative reporting of events in Odessa, Crimea, and also eastern Ukraine. Evidently, according to their logic, everything has started because of journalists and has nothing to do with politicians.
